\Block{The Real-Imag to Complex Block}{ri\_to\_c}{ritoc}{Aaron Parsons}{Aaron Parsons}{Concatenates real and imaginary inputs into a complex output. Useful for simplifying interconnects. See also: Complex to Real-Imag Block (c\_to\_ri, \ref{ctori})}



\begin{ParameterTable}



\end{ParameterTable}



